

chgrp                        Command                        chgrp




Change the group owner of files

cchhggrrpp _g_r_o_u_p _f_i_l_e ...

chgrp changes  the group owner of each file  to group.  The group
may be specified by a valid group name or a valid numerical group
identifier.

Only the superuser may use chgrp.

***** Files *****

/eettcc/ggrroouupp -- Convert group name to group identifier

***** See Also *****

chmod, chown, commands







































